online.game.sgf
Class sgf_node

java.lang.Object
  online.game.sgf.sgf_node
All Implemented Interfaces:
sgf_names
public class sgf_node
extends java.lang.Object
implements sgf_names

sgf_node contains a list of properties which are part of the node, and a second list of auxiliary properties which are for the client application to use any way it wants; for example, to keep track of active information as the node is used to display a game.
